sentences: Anne Lise Frøkedal known by her stage name Frøkedal is a folk-pop, singer-songwriter from Norway.
Releasing a series of singles and an EP in 2015, she released her debut album Hold On Dreamer in 2016.
In 2017, Frøkedal announced her return with the release of singles Stranger, and double single LTF/Cracks.
Frøkedal released her second album, 'How We Made It' on August 31, 2018.
